{"tid":1046401,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有錢人船p，窮柒毒撚勿入","createTime":"2019-03-04T08:24:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T23:41:52.000Z","uid":49124,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a745883e231e0d23b5fabfd9e411388cbb81d0","tid":1046401,"uid":49124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:24:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個星期五，我唔去浦了。夜晚出海。&nbsp;<br />\n我地book 了3 隻船。第一隻Black Pearl，搶的<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/161205_7826e431340b153c08d0075d9b24f03f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F161205_7826e431340b153c08d0075d9b24f03f.jpg&h=01d96064&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/161352_dd7d69b3b0016cce2756f61b951df157.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F161352_dd7d69b3b0016cce2756f61b951df157.jpg&h=70b7bdcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐50人的，長80幾呎。 <br />\n<br />\n另一隻, 私伙的 Pi's Boat 坐40人，印度風遊艇，有野生動物觀賞/體驗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/161706_5a2fb2a04781d9449d00abee5b89df39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F161706_5a2fb2a04781d9449d00abee5b89df39.jpg&h=e513c655&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/161740_78dc473711ba0a4f2fc8c896e449bb9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F161740_78dc473711ba0a4f2fc8c896e449bb9e.jpg&h=98d542d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/161933_0e2a24085f6902d2eb52e6e713628d10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F161933_0e2a24085f6902d2eb52e6e713628d10.jpg&h=cf230c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/04/161953_d750abee8db2938018aa3fba3b71c3ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F04%2F161953_d750abee8db2938018aa3fba3b71c3ab.jpg&h=9a9b37b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢隻多d，入少少，有動物玩有風景，寫意d。 重有一隻普通中式船，要自己划。 搞手會買好多酒。 星期五 , 7點尖沙咀碼頭集合 <br />\n男仔：$1000 位&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女仔：Model , 靚女 , 鬼妹免費。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去船河的人吧。 <br />\np.s. 呢d船河算平，搞手只係執翻少少搵食，最緊要大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"047cdc55361dfd9d2e1582bcf0521b68efd7fda3","tid":1046401,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92a0be99ea2c1b900198b5c77885394b1e1bdb57","tid":1046401,"uid":49124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"047cdc55361dfd9d2e1582bcf0521b68efd7fda3","tid":1046401,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:30:50.000Z","msg":"我地搞手有考慮到呢個問題，所以禦寒方面你地可以放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw肥絲你唔比去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cdf783d421b0bfd4a936126f71812046381cee9","tid":1046401,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"926d84bc9ea79aa743baba77e4025add80788f6c","tid":1046401,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"7cdf783d421b0bfd4a936126f71812046381cee9","tid":1046401,"uid":122570,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T08:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 